---
import fcLogo from "../assets/fc_logo.svg";
import guardianLogo from "../assets/guardian_logo.svg";
import reutersLogo from "../assets/reuters_logo.svg";
---

<div class="py-20 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span
        class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm font-mono tracking-wider mb-4"
      >
        PRESS & RECOGNITION
      </span>
      <p class="text-gray-600 font-light text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our work has been featured in leading publications and recognized for
        its impact on data accessibility and intelligence systems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12"
    >
      <a
        href="https://www.fastcompany.com/91294411/trump-removed-an-online-tool-that-predicts-your-climate-risk-rogue-data-scientists-rebuilt-it"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="flex justify-center md:justify-end group cursor-pointer p-4 transition-all hover:scale-105"
      >
        <img
          src={fcLogo.src}
          alt="Fast Company Logo"
          class="h-8 w-auto opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all invert group-hover:brightness-110"
        />
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/ng-interactive/2025/mar/26/extreme-weather-risk-tool-fema-trump"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="flex justify-center group cursor-pointer p-4 transition-all hover:scale-105"
      >
        <img
          src={guardianLogo.src}
          alt="Guardian Logo"
          class="h-12 w-auto opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all group-hover:brightness-110"
        />
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://www.context.news/digital-rights/volunteers-on-right-side-of-history-fight-trump-data-purge"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="flex justify-center md:justify-start group cursor-pointer p-4 transition-all hover:scale-105"
      >
        <img
          src={reutersLogo.src}
          alt="Reuters Logo"
          class="h-12 w-auto opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all group-hover:brightness-110"
        />
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-light italic">
        "Fulton Ring restored critical public access to climate risk data when
        government tools were removed, preserving and rebuilding intelligence
        systems that help communities understand their vulnerability to extreme
        weather."
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
